name: Erica Durance
description:
Erica Durance is a Canadian actress known for her roles as Lois Lane on the superhero television series Smallville (2004–2011) and as Dr. Alex Reid on the medical drama series Saving Hope (2012–2017)

A favorite actress of mine and I primarily used images from her Smallville days to train with. Hope to see what everyone comes up with using this TI so until next time!
